# ISRASKI
Premium Hebrew-RTL ski packages site (Gudauri, Georgia). Israeli audience. Hebrew only.

**Stack:** `index.html` only — HTML + `<style>` + `<script>`. Google Fonts (Noto Serif Hebrew, Rubik, Montserrat) + local `fonts/`. No build tools.

**Files:** `sections/01-hero/` (hero-bg.webp, logo.png) · `sections/02-packages/` (pkg-*.jpg) · `server.ps1`

**Colors:** Alpine Night `#060d1e` · Ice Blue `#a8c8f0` · Glacier Gold `rgba(235,200,100,...)` · Summit White `#f5f8fc` · Hero heading `clamp(2.4rem,5.6vw,4.4rem)`

**Sections:** Hero · Why Gudauri · Why ISRASKI · Packages · Gallery · Testimonials · FAQ · CTA Strip · Footer

**Rules:**
- `dir="rtl"` everywhere. No English in UI.
- Never scan `C:\Users\User` recursively. Never rename media files — verify exact name before `src`.
- No new CSS/JS files. No build tools.
- After edit: state what changed + "רענן index.html".
- New image needed → ask user to copy manually, state expected filename.
- Short answers (1 sentence). No clarification requests — show 2-3 variants when unsure.
